@jaden
Could you look at 2 FE human review related bugs?

1. NoneType error in the attached screenshot. 
> *Prateek Tenkale*  [12:06 PM]
> Steps to reproduce Nonetype _use ibdoc error:
> 
> With multiple_paystubs more.pdf:
> 1. We have { records 0 | page nums [1, 2, 3] } { record 1 | page nums [4, 5, 6] }
> 2. Select pages 1 and 2, and click create document
> 3. When re-extracting fields for the new document it will throw an error `/change-classification-label`
> 4. Payload `record_index=-1`
2. Error: parsed.slice(...).map is not a function. Auto-save is disabled after 3 failed attempts to save. ...

Second one I have a PR up for it yesterday just waiting for review https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/74543
